        <item>
            <title>【評測】Threezero《心橋鏈結》小糰　高性價比 + 連動設計有心思</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/31/mdlxdango/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mdlxdango</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/31/mdlxdango/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 05:00:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1217960</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Threezero 的出品超越來越多不同系列，今次推出的《Kokone Link（心橋鏈接）》系列首款產品，名為「Dango（小糰）」的小型機械人。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217962" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/snap0174-694x477.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="477" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/snap0174-694x477.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/snap0174.jpg 1209w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a title="_DSC6431" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53498290084/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53498290084_24d80bc104_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6431" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>此 Figure 取材自網絡科幻小説，並以 1:1 比例製作，完美復刻小説中角色原貌。小糰高約 9 釐米，其外觀設計以白、藍、金色調為主，以光面漆作塗裝，特別是金色部份，很多細節及紋理都有表現出來，效果非常不錯可見廠方的用心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217963" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6273-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6273-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6273.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217964" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6276-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6276-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6276.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>小糰的體積雖然細小，但當中卻設有總共 49 個關節，擁有合金骨架，部份部件也是合金製，雖然細細隻但手感都幾有份量，且保持良好可動性，關節也幾扎實。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217965" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6302-412x580.jpg" alt="" width="412" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6302-412x580.jpg 412w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6302.jpg 640w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 412px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217966" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6309-452x580.jpg" alt="" width="452" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6309-452x580.jpg 452w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6309.jpg 702w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 452px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217967" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6304-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6304-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6304.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217968" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6305-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6305-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6305.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217969" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6307-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6307-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6307.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217970" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6312-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6312-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6312.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217975" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6455-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6455-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6455.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217974" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6320-429x580.jpg" alt="" width="429" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6320-429x580.jpg 429w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6320.jpg 666w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 429px" /></p><p>其中一個亮點是小糰的眼球設計是可動的，可擺出可愛的 Pose；頭頂被拉起時，就轉換為戰鬥模式，連動式設計會令眼蓋半閉，耳邊的盔甲會展開；前額透明部份及雙眼亦有 LED 燈，啟動後加上戰鬥模式，設計非常有心思，令小編不得不讚。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217973" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_3028-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_3028-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_3028.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217971" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6314-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6314-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6314.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217972" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6317-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6317-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6317.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>其他 Pose</h2><p><a title="_DSC6297" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53498290209/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53498290209_6aab1e580d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6297" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC6321" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53498290104/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53498290104_94026a91fd_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6321" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC6351" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53497987041/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53497987041_024d445533_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6351" width="1024" height="694" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC6464 (1)" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53499531314/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53499531314_8bd0e3c5d0_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6464 (1)" width="1024" height="792" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC6452 (1)" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53498342627/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53498342627_e10dd7291d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6452 (1)" width="957" height="1024" /></a></p><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC6461 (1)" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53498342622/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53498342622_e842a84c13_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6461 (1)" width="873" height="1024" /></a></p><p>配件方面，小糰附有 4 Set 可換手勢，及兩款特效配件「藍色光劍」與「黃色光炮」，提供更多互動性及可玩性。最具創意特別地方，附有一個鎖匙扣配件，插好在背後，可將小糰變身成為裝飾或鎖匙扣。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217978" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6470-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6470-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6470.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217979" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6471-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6471-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6471.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217980" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6472-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6472-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6472.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217976" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6474-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6474-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6474.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217977" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6475-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6475-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6475.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>今次 Threezero 的小糰是一個新的嘗試，雖然《Kokone Link（心橋鏈接）》這套小説不是太多人認識，但也見到廠方製作上的用心及誠意，而這個 Figure 的定價只是$200 有找 (早鳥預訂優惠至 2 月 2 日)，可説非常抵玩高性價比。相信之後亦會有其他機體登場，期待這個新系列的發展。</p><p><a title="_DSC6333" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53498141863/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53498141863_4c0bfa6219_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6333" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/31/mdlxdango/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/">【評測】Threezero《心橋鏈結》小糰　高性價比 + 連動設計有心思</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
